  <LINE>MEDICAL AND SCIENTIFIC INSTITUTIONS.</LINE>
  <LINE>HUTCHESON'S HOSPITAL AND SCHOOL.</LINE>
  <LINE>Founded by George and Thomas Hutclieson in</LINE>
  <LINE>1639 and 1641, for the maintenance of decayed</LINE>
  <LINE>burgesses of Glasgow, and the widows and daughters</LINE>
  <LINE>of burgesses; and the education of boys, sons and</LINE>
  <LINE>grandsons of burgesses.</LINE>
